PlotNParticles <- uds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = tot_nparticles, y = depth, col = profile)) +
 facet_wrap(~project) +
 geom_point(alpha = 0.3, shape = 1) +
scale_y_reverse() + scale_x_log10()
